Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.39,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.47,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:37.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.11,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:15.25,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:22.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.33,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:34.27,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder whether you should know the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery, you see. They had to remove one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years... When a relapse occurs within five years... there isn't really any hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I left the man I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether I have a long life left before me or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a burden in my loved one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that, because I loved him, I had no choice but to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that it was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that I should never have told you all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... it's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't related by blood, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...the two of you seem alike, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I could talk to you about this because you're Takehiko-san's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,S... sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Little sister? You mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... I'm really my brother's little sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,37. Merry-Go-Round
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry! I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were writing letters to him and all, so I just thought that you must have known...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't know! I didn't know about it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well you see, Takehiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa... Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a bit late, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I pour you some fresh tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I think I'm going to take a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Down to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... er, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, dear. Don't worry about her. I'll call Tomoko-san in a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... okay. Could you, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...I received a call from Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's decided to study abroad in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's leaving it up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time for Nanako to learn about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you feel is best, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I didn't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt so mixed up inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saint-Juste-sama's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaoru-no-Kimi's love and the scars, both physical and emotional...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And on top of that, there is the matter between the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like the whole world has turned upside down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takehiko-san is Professor Misonoo's son by his previous wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I think that Nanako might be hurt to learn of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a kindhearted girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were to learn that I abandoned Takehiko and his mother, she would really be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't {\i1}abandon{\i0} them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the circumstances, that's what it amounts to in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I just don't have the courage to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just afraid that Nanako will hate me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No... no, that won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there. 'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At any rate... at any rate, I've decided to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll ask Papa about the truth; I figure that I'll have time to think over it more after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go for a walk, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the place, Nanako. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you and I first met, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The place where Papa and I first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time you saw me, you looked like you were afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were just standing there looking at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,From that point on, you were my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My one and only daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, precious Nanako... your Papa has only ever once told you a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, there was something I never told you, which amounts to the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... I have a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a child with the woman I was with before I married your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's about seven years older than you. He is your step-brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be honest with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...even though it's been thirteen years since I saw him last...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...I love my son every bit as much as I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in my thoughts always, just as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from this one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly feel that I've been the Papa that you always considered me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see him again, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, if... if you had said that you didn't love my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you had turned out to be that sort of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't know what I would have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa... Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...it was so sunny in the morning, but it turned rainy in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, I went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went out; I just couldn't stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to see you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... what happened? You're totally soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, when it snowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it that day, when it was snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That snowy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The last class day of the cram school course...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ok everyone, you have five minutes to work this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You had been teaching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our last day together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had made up my mind to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was silly; I was really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have a question? Okay. Which page?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}P... p-please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a lover, or even a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...just... I thought... if you would just read my letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,May I say it one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... you really are my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so mean of you, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa told me, you know. "Takehiko knew all along that you were his little sister."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't very nice of you, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I did intend to tell you, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When? Well, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... well, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel of you, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If... if I hadn't ever found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I had just continued writing to you like this, then eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...eventually... the letters alone wouldn't have been enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If... if I'd really fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...what would you have done about it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't ever actually dated a boy yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I were to do so, I imagine that he'd find me to be the {\i1}persistent{\i0} type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I knew from the start that you were my younger sister, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not related by blood, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I'd started feeling that way, it wouldn't have mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... er... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You really had me going there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Once again, it is raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day that's important to me somehow, it ends up raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that way, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it was raining on that day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was raining that day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was hoping to catch a glimpse of my father, who had left me and my mother to remarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was standing there, in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, I saw you for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You looked so very precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You had dirt all over your hands, and you were holding a little red shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You gazed at me with those lovely eyes as you spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was it, no more than five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye-bye! Come see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That faraway day... that rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may have forgotten, but I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misonoo Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From that day forward... I had a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nanako..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... no... could I call you "Nanako-kun" from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happiest if you called me "Nanako".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...you really were my brother. Henmi Takehiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A really, truly wonderful brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Longed after by Fukiko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Loved by Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those enchanting, dark brown eyes, sparkling now just as they did in that day so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother... I'm glad that I am your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that it's a good thing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, no matter how wonderful you may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as my brother, you could never really love me in a romantic way... unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll keep writing letters to you, the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'll do my best to write even more, as many and as often as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, sooner or later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...sooner or later, I'm sure, we'll run across one another again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know where yet, but I'll see those dark brown eyes of yours again someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heh heh heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been able to write it all down, through happiness and heartache...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...through confusion and uncertainty, all my bittersweet trials...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...everything, in my own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}P.S. Of course, I can't send you{\i0} this {\i1}letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nope, I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Henmi here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No trouble. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only called because I have something that I need to apologize to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have quite a few things that I'd like to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that she knew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and so inadvertently told Misonoo-san that she is your younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry; I did something that I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... I want to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The carousel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's ride the carousel again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Out beyond the carousel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...out past the spinning sky-planes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I can see it. I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it? What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future! Everything from here on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With one turn. I see myself tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The second time around, I see myself the day after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the third pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...this "future you," what's she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She loves Takehiko-san even more tomorrow than she does today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day after that, she loves you even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With each passing day, she loves you even more than the day before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better stop that carousel before we get carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll never get it to stop! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sounds like I'm in trouble, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...no matter how many times the carousel goes around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't see anything on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, the gentleman with the appointment is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you must be busy today; thank you for having the time to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've decided to study at the University of Schellenberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a letter of recommendation and a guarantor's voucher, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you would be so kind, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them to you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If that will be all, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... yes, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly, thank you so very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we walk together as far as the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! Well, let's get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's it up to now, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,185 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... you've grown so much in the thirteen years since I last saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I have to go off that way now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Takehiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:14.11,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:19.58,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:25.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:30.66,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:36.94,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.94,0:24:42.41,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:45.14,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:47.95,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:50.35,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.35,0:24:55.62,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.43,0:25:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.18,0:25:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru continues to obstinately refuse Henmi's love, thinking only of his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko tries to convince Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.64,0:25:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that Saint-Juste wanted her to keep thinking of living to live her life to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode: Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.28,0:25:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother... there is no end to my tears...
